Snake
=====


Introduction
------------

This is a simple game snake wrote as a platform to implement different snake AI.


Requirements
------------

- Lua 5.3
- Lua-SDL2 (luarocks install lua-sdl2)
  https://github.com/Tangent128/luasdl2/


Usage
-----

Play the game:
> lua main.lua

Or give a brain to the snake:
> lua main.lua -b brains/blind.lua -x 10 -y 10


